snippet.title: Why Won't My Perfume Last F/ Dossier Ambery Saffron Perfume Review.
snippet.description:
Welcome Back to my channel!!
Have you ever wondered why your perfume won't last throughout the day? Even your most treasured perfume purchases that seem to smell so beautiful in the bottle won't give you the same payoff just moments after applying it. Why does the same perfume that you smelled on a friend smells horribly on you??

#perfumereviews #whywontmyperfumelast #Dossier 

If you had ANY of these same questions any have yet to get a proper answer. Stay tuned to this video to have your questions answered as well as learn about Dossier.co a luxury perfume company that provides all the luxury scents without the luxury prices!

https://dossier.co

For 10% off use Discount Code "Letitia10" for the month of August!


Foundations Shades:
Gucci Foundation 410w
Fenty Beauty Foundation 420
Huda Beauty Faux Filter Foundation 500g Mocha
Laura Mercier Tinted Moisturizer Broad Spectrum SPF 20 6C1 Walnut
Rare Beauty Liquid Touch Weightless Foundation 460w
Too Faced Born This Way Foundation Matte or Original (Chai) Spiced Rum
Estee Lauder Double Wear Foundation 6W1 Sandlewood
Anastasia Beverly Hills Luminous Foundation 480C
